\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would you give me your full name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Frederick Arthur Randall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And your present address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Room 16, Abbots Hospital, but it should be Trinity Hospital.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh should it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's what its known by the postal addresses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 It's only a local name - Abbots Hospital, and in the telephone directory it's Trinity Hospital.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. And are you a widower.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And can you remember the year of your marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 1924.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 The year of your birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 19 - 1894.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. And where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Guildford. At White Hill - Brides Hill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Brides Hill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's one of the hills that are - well their just missing now it's - er.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - off Sydenham Road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Off Sydenham Road - that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233  from
 there - I lived there - I should think I went there when I was about five and I stopped there - I was twenty eight when I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So you lived there twenty eight years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Five - twenty-three years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh twenty-three years. You went there when you were five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. I remember it was twenty-three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So the house you were born in you only lived in for five years of your life, is that right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh no. The house I was born in was where I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233  from.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233  at 
twenty-eight so you must have lived there twenty-eight years, unless you went away in between.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No I never went away.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So I think you were there about twenty eight years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Roughly about twenty eight years, I know it was twenty four when I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 It was - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And that was in Bright Hill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Yes - it could have been thirty years - see wait a minute - hang on now - five - what it really means is five from thirty - twenty five years I should say - wouldn't it - roughly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And then did your family stay there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, they stayed there 'til 1930.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see - so they didn't move at all while you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No they didn't move at all, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
I had one brother - he's ten years older than me - he'd be round about the eighty-five now - of course he's gone - he never lived long after the 1914 war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And I've got a sister living today. Down the old people's bungalows. She must be about - well turned eighty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 She is how old?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 She must be about eighty-three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Eighty-three?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And she's your only sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's all - she's the only one - there was only three of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And how old are you now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I was seventy-five last August.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So that your sister is older than you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You were the youngest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see. Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Now wait a moment - I should think roughly about 36.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I wouldn't be sure - I think he was a Midhurst man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 He was a ....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 A Midhurst man - Sussex.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh, he came from Midhurst, Sussex?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - but he came here very young like - er .......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 He came here very young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 He was here before he was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Ooh yes - he came here when he was a boy, oh yes, when he was a boy, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And when he grew up what was his occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Well he was at the Friary Brewery for some considerable time - in the tun room. And then he left there and he went to the railway and that's where he finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see. Did he ever have any other jobs before the brewery job, do you remember? Would you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 He could have worked for Chaplins a little while before.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Is that a removal firm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 But I don't remember him doing that. I'm only going by what my people tell me, you see?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did he have any casual or part time jobs as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And did he ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not while he was - um - not until he become 65. When he become 65 he done quite a bit of work for Philpott in Chan}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12600013\charrsid14556233 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 ry View Road. The old gentleman - not the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes - was that Mr H R Philpott's father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's right - I can - I remember his father when he was head waiter at the Lion. Mr Philpott's father, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And what did he do - he just helped in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, he laid the lawn for him - he got out all the chalk and he laid the lawn. And then - I got - you want to ask me some more questions.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. What did he do in the railway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 He was a toolman.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What is that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well it - er - er - when they used to go to the workshop ... they used to require any and he used to serve out the 
particular tools that they wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see. Do you remember your father ever being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How old was your mother when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well she was about - my father would have been about 36 when I was born and my mother was a year younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, about 35?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Littleton. That's on the Portsmouth road by St Catherine's - just laying at the back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Had she any jobs before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I couldn't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she work after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes. She used to do - er - a lot of work for Spiers }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1001383 &}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233  Ponds that time of day - when they done all the station catering - and she used to do all the waitresses aprons and the caps - I can see her now with the old flat irons, you know - and-
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she do this at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes. She done it at home yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was that a full time job or part time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Only a part time job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How many hours would she work at that? Have you any idea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well -
 I've known her up at twelve o'clock night to finish and get up in the morning before six o'clock to get my father off to work. Long day wasn't it? Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 With a family too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she continue to do work during her }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233  life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No not - er - for, you know, not for too long because she suffered with eczema so bad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - and it was on her hands and her face. Just an unfortunate part, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So she didn't have other work later on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When you grew up.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 None whatever - no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 If mother worked after she had children, who looked after the children when she had to go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 She never went out to work they always bought the work to her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 They always bought the work to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So she didn't even have to deliver it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Can I ask you now about your life at home when you were a child? A time up to when you left school? How many rooms were there in the house in Bright Hill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Four. Two downstairs and two bedrooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did anyone else besides your parents and brothers and sisters live in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No one else bar our own family. Never did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your mother pay anyone to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was the washing done at home or sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Yes. My mother always done it although she suffered with her hands terrible - she always done it. But she had to wash herself in bran, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 This was to help ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Had to wash her face in bran yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your mother or father mend or make the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. Can't say they did - she used to repair but never make. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would you get them new or would you sometimes get them secondhand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - we got them new admitted - my mother did
n't like secondhand stuff, but we had - my mother had to pay a shilling a week for them off of what we called at that time of day a tally man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see - and then when she'd paid enough she could buy something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were they always brought in this way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That time of day, eighty per cent of the working man's was. Eighty per cent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And in your family, were they all bought that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Shoes? Well we used to get them off the same people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So your clothes and your shoes for the family all came off this man called the tally man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Very of - well as a matter of fact - whe
n she went - used to go - have to go in St Thomas's Hospital in London he used to look after us and cook our food of a Sunday - the weekends - cook the Sunday dinner and all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So that would be cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And do the h
ousework when he got home at nights, you know what I mean, oh yes. Well my mother was - used to go as much as - away as long as a month at a time and they never could do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Never made any success of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And when she was at home, did he ever help her with the housework as well by perhaps doing the fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 In every way, my father helped my mother - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 With washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes and everything, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Like cleaning or cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. In every way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. He - I can see him papering the - ceiling and the walls now, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about repairs, who would do those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, the landlord - when you could get them done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was that difficult?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 The water was - used to run down the walls but y
ou couldn't do nothing about it. You had to keep the fires going to keep it out a bit, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, my oldest brother used to make the cupboards - there was only shelves in there but my eldest brother w
as pretty useful. And he used to make the cupboards to hide - to hide the bare walls behind the shelves, you know, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your father ever help with the children by dressing or undressing you or bathing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - I don't think so, no he never used to do that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did he ever used to read to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did he ever tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did he ever take you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not a lot because because of - he wanted - we used to go down the Pompey an
d down through the dockyards so - um - go over Pompey - well I call it Pompey but it's Portsmouth now, you know what I mean. Oh yes, didn't used to cost much then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That was one of your treats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, but my mother always used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, funny thing you should mention that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your father ever look after you when your mother was out apart from when she had to be in hospital?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. No, my mother always took that on her own like, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see. Did you have any tasks you had to carry out regularly at home to help your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Well - I used to have to help my father do a bit of gardening, you know, when I - before I left school. But - er - me being the youngest one I suppose they didn't press me li
ke they did the older ones. I almost done as I liked - played a lot of football in me young days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, what did your brother and sister do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 My brother was apprenticed to one of the oldest basket firms in Guildford and they're still today. He was
 apprenticed at Cobbetts. Right down - right down the bottom of the town that were then - on the river bridge - now they're in the Sydenham Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes I know they are. What did he do to help your mother and father in the home apart from making the cupboards as you told me?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Well - he was a good boy to my mother - he was a good boy, yes - 'cos we never had a lot of money then Madam, to help your mother I mean to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No I wasn't thinking of money, I was thinking of working in the home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh he was - he was very handy and very good in - far better than I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh, far better than I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What did your sister do to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, she - went out to work when she was fourteen. She - the first job she ..
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When she was at home did she have regular things to do to help your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes. But she wasn't too clever at it - she didn't want it - didn't like it .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 She didn't like doing it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did the older children help the young
er ones with the things they found difficult, like dressing or eating or look after them in other ways when you were small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not so much as it is today. Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did the younger children help the older in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I shouldn't think so - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Ye - well my people weren't so strict as some - some were very strict. But we had to be in bed by nine o'clock. So I .......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your mother put you to bed or ........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 At what age did you put yourself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Oh we used to go upstairs - I was about eight I suppose - we got knowledge to undress ourselves and get right into bed then, oh yes, mother used to come up and I remember her saying 'now say your prayers', you know, I can see it now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you share a bedroom or bed with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I slept with my brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 In the same bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. And my sister slept in the same bedroom as my mother and father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 We never had one - my mother used to put us in the copper Friday night - the boys and Saturday night my sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And when did you have clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh every Monday - well - I wouldn't be sure - Sunday - Sunday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Sunday morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes, that's right - Sunday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Where?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Where? Oh in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And were there any occasions when they sat and had a meal in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Only high days and holidays we used - we called it, you know what that means, Madam, high days and holidays, yes - and - er -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes and then what would you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Anything special, you know, anybody coming and that, we went in the front.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 In the front room, would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 In the kitchen - on the - on an open fireplace.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 A coal range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 My mother never had a - she never had a range as we know it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You mean not a gas cooker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - but not a coal range.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What she had was an open fireplace and an oven on the left hand side.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And of course there was no hot water system?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh, none whatever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When was your breakfast eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What time was your breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh our breakfast was always ready at seven o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And what member of the family would be there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Us three boys - father had gone to work. Us three children like, you know, two boys and a girl. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And what did he do for his first meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh he got up and got his self.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 He got some himself before he went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What did you usually eat and drink for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well we used to have some porridge and we mostly had a rasher of bacon, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What would you have to drink?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh, tea. Didn't know what coffee was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What would you have for your mid-day meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I used to go down the butchers and get sixpennyworth
 of what we called beef pieces - and that was enough - as much as we pay four and five bob today for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes I can well believe that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Sixpennyworth of beef pieces and we had a damn good meat pudding and we had a bit left for tomorrow and my mother 
never stinted me. When they talk about the bad old times - not in the food game. As regards the money - yes - but when it comes to food we were better fed than what they are because it was good food - real good food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about the evening meal, what would you have had for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh, we generally used to have a basin of soup, yes, and then a cup of cocoa. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would you have anything different on certain days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes. We had a .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What would they be? Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Sundays we
 had a cooked joint 3/8 and then - 'course we had a big joint for half a crown - a big joint - and there was five of us and we had what we wanted - cold on the Monday. Then my mother used to hash it up and make a good old shepherds pie. And then she used 
t
o send me down the shop maybe on the Wednesday get sixpennyworth of liver that lasted us for a couple of days and then on about - on a Saturday very often - we used to go and get sixpennyworth of chitterlings and they were twopence a pound. Mmm. I went to
 .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about the evening meal on Sundays or Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh evening meals on Sundays we always had a meat between bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So that was a special day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That was a luxury, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your mother or father bake their own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she make her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - I don't remember my mother doing that - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she bottle fruit? Or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - because her hands was her trouble, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would that apply to to making pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
No - she used to make pickles and - er - pickled cabbage and pickled onions. Well what we called - I don't know if they call them today - we called 'em shallots. I ........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 They're smaller, aren't they?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would she ever make any home made wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Or any home herbal remedy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7611384\charrsid14556233 No my mother was a strict tee}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 totaller.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about home made medicines like herbal remedies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Any beer brewed for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. My father used to have a go now and again - I don't think he made much of a success of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your father or mother grow their own vegetables and fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - my father did - but we had no fruit - we had an allotment on wh
at they call today - on the long fields - that is - er - up Pewley Way and right along as if you was going to St Marcus.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I know, near Pewley Downs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they have to buy any vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Never. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 But they would have to buy fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, we would have to buy fruit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about tinned? Did you ever have any tinned vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 None whatever. Didn't know what they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Tinned fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Never knew what they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you keep any livestock for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Yes - rabbits. And I even kept tame rats. White rats with pink eyes - and I even took them to school and the master lectured on them and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Those were pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Hens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 My father kept a few but not a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not pigs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no, nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Who looked after the animals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh my father. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How many times a week did you eat meat? Most days I think you said.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh Sunday and Monday and Tuesday, you see. Hot, cold and then what we called a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7611384\charrsid14556233 shepherd\rquote s pie}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 . Three days a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Still meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 But no tinned .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I think we - er - had meat five days a week. If you call liver meat. See what I mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about tinned meat? Did you ever have tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, I don't remember it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever get some extra meat, such as a rabbit from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh, yes, we often used to go over a long fields.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you get those yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Over old Whitey's field - oh yes - we used to - put wires down. And mushrooms we used to go about five o'clock in the morning and get a fish basket full.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would this be your father and your brother and yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. My father didn't know we went - and didn't want - I don't think he wanted to, you know, what .... well my father used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And how often would you do this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh not too regular because they'd rumbled us, you see?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember seeing your mother having less food so that the family could have more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Many and many a time, yes, she'd sooner give it to us and go short herself, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your father have a larger helping than the rest of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. He was a big man - he worked pretty hard, you know, but he didn't want it but he always had it, you know - he didn't want ........

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were you allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - definitely not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh we had to eat a bit of everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What was your parents attitude if you left some food uneaten on the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, my mother wasn't - er - what can I - wasn't a nasty woman, you know what
 I mean, she wouldn't lay the law down to you, but she didn't like it all the same, but she wouldn't say so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So you wouldn't feel very happy about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 If there was something on the table you wanted, like the salt, could yo
u ask somebody to pass it to you, or did you have to wait until it was offered to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh we'd ask somebody to pass it, but we didn't dare to put our arm up and in front like they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh, yes. If it was there we had it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have to sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes we had to sit at the table properly, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Could you bring toys and a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When - when everybody had finished their meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You all waited until the last person had finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I think you said that all the family sat at the table for the meal if they were all at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes that's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So that nobody had it separately?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - but of course when my sister went out to work she lived in you see - so what it meant there was only us two boys there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you always sit at the same places at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How was the meal served, was it served by your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And what order would you be served in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - I think my father came first - us children and my mother last.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And can you remember where you sat before you could feed yourself? Would you Have your meal with the rest of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes in a high chair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You had a high chair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 With the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - sitting up ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 At the same table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh, yes at the table, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, very easy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you feel close to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well it's a funny question to ask, isn't it - er - I always felt closer to my father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I can't say why. My m
other was a good woman and I've got nothing to say in any way - but I must be honest - I always leant towards my father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your mother show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh, yes - very deep but for my oldest brother mostly, because he was a little bit on the del
icate side and as I got older I can understand why, see what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 If you'd had any worries could you share them with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I don't know as we had any real worries not us children that time of day. We never done the silly things that these
 people do now. We had to behave ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would you ever go to your father with any ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh no, he always sent us back to mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 We had to do as we was told.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in certain ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 As far as it was possible - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they say you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 My father did, yes, definitely, he said always stand up for yourself, boy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you and your brother and sister would grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I don't - I can't answer that question because I really do not know honestly - no doubt 
they had ambitions but they kept them to themselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents bring you up to consider certain things important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - now then - in this way - always raise your hat to}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7611384\charrsid14556233 
 a lady a little bit above your}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 self - and when you see the Parson, touch your hat and the Doctor and the District Visitor and all like that you know - the Church people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And did they feel that some things were right and some things were wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 In what way, Madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, I suppose, in how you behaved to other people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Oh they always told us if it - if they thought we were wrong - but they didn't - used to - my people never laid the law down to us, if you understand my meaning - they spoke to us in a common sense way expecting us to know what they told us see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, pretty poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. Definitely not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 If you did something that your parents disapproved of, what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Something they didn't approve of? Well my father used to get the belt - without any hesitation, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And was it always your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Always - my mother never laid a hand on us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would that be often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - not often - he was a pretty lenient man - but if it was bad we had it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember any particular occasion when you were punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Ooh I know we got over the top of Harvey Road now what used to be called the Green Road and he used to be apple trees there and we got scrumping there and a copper come to my father and said 'here your two boys been up there }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7611384\charrsid14556233 fil}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
ching' and he said, well he said 'All right, I'll give 'em just a little bit of a belt' he said 'they won't do it any more' - and we never done it no more. He didn't used to be cruel with it but he just, you know, just reminded us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember how you felt about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh pretty sore - more ways than one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You were physically sore but did your feel rather resentful?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - I didn't feel resentful because we knew he was right, you know what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You thought you deserved it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Would you say that you received the ideas you had about how to behave from both your parents, or did one play a more important part than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - my mother impressed on us how to behave but my father made us how - behave, you know what I mean. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have anything special to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. My mother always used to make an ice cake or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have any friends in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes, children, yes, our own age, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Can you remember anything you did with your mother or father together on Christmas day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Oh yes - they - my father never used to go out Christmas Day - always used to stop in with the children and he used to have all the decorations up round the ceiling and all the old twigs ro
und the mantelpiece and the candles in - on the trees in the windows and we used to light them and we used to have the old cylinder records that time of day - the round ones like that used to fit on a cylinder - not the flat ones - er - a phonograph - we 
used to play that all day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So you had a good time at Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have any other musical instruments in the home apart from this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - wouldn't call it a musical instrument - but my brother used to play in the Chur
ch Lads Brigade - he used to play - he was a drummer but he used to have a go with the cornet sometimes and the people next door complained about it so my mother stopped him at that - they didn't mid the drums but they didn't want the cornet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was there anyone in the family who sang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. No, no none whatever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes - snakes and ladders and dominoes and draughts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they ever play anything other - out of doors with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. No not as I know, no. Certain they didn't.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were there books in the House?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, there wasn't in our house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, newspapers, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7611384\charrsid14556233 Magazines}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Er - one or two but not much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember your mother or father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, I don't think I do. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they ever read aloud to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 They did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they ever read aloud to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - not as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember a funeral in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What do you mean - in our family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When you were a child.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, I remember going to my uncle's funeral. He went - he came home from the Boer War and - er - I suppose he died at about 1906.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see. Who would go to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh - er - my mother and my father and any other brothers and sisters and even the children would go, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would you wear special clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh we - you had to wear black then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You had to wear black?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Ooh it was terrible to go to a funeral if you didn't wear black.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And the children too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Well - no - not the children - the actual parents, you know, but the children used to have black tie on and all like that - but, ooh it was a terrible thing to go to a funeral without black.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were you taken out visiting neighbours, friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Only relations - never to friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 My mother used to take us there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were you taken shopping?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - well my sister used to do the shopping, you see. My mother never done any shopping much - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Your sister used to do the shopping for your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever go out with just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 With just your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 More so my mother than my father, yes, if we had to go and visit our aunty which was being her sister - my mother used to take us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see, and you would go just on your own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember any other outings with your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Ooh - going to Portsmouth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Going to Portsmouth - when would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's all - that's the only seaside place we knew - Portsmouth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would that be on a bank holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Mostly Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Mostly Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Mmmm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So these expeditions to Portsmouth would be the only holiday you would have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And you would for the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I used to go away with me aunty at Aldershot. When my mother was in hospital.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Your aunty looked after you when your mother was away
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's about the only time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Ooh Saturday mornings? Ooh - used to get up go and do the shopping for my mother, com
e back - get on an old pair of football boots and go up on the fields and stop up there 'til dinner time - then come back - see a football match in the afternoon always. It were a proper happy day for us youngsters, yes, yes, Saturdays, yes. I never had t
o clean no knives and forks like a lot of people did, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh we had to go to Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have different clothes on Sundays?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not Sundays - no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents think it wrong to ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 To play games on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about working on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well they had to work didn't they? My father had to work Sundays. See, and he had to go in 'til twelve o'clock Sundays
. Twelve o'clock mid-day. There was no option, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents attend a place of worship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 My mother used to go to St Nicholas' Church pretty regular but not my father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would she go most Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, oh yes - she used to
 go - had a communion service that time of day, at half past seven in the morning. Used to be about - well not much over half hour I don't think. It wasn't a communal service that you - they got over here in the churches - but it was a communion service.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you attend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh I used to go to church, yes, yes, but - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 As well as Sunday school -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, but I mustn't say I went a lot because I wouldn't be telling the truth - but I had to go to Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You had to go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were there any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - we used to go to the seaside with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see, that would be for the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What other social activities would be organised by - would the Sunday school be St Nicholas' Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Ooh - that was very - er - pretty er - well there was a lot of denominations but I should think the biggest one in Guildford was the Congregational.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was it - which one did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Which Sunday School did you go to?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I went to Holy Trinity. O
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. But the Congregational - when they - when their Sunday school went they had over a hundred children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever go with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. No. They always kept theirselves apart - it's very funny - religion - they get - they never mixed in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did the church run any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - I belonged to the Band of Hope.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What did you do in the Band of Hope?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well we used to go down of a Monday night and - er - Now the day is over - I can remember that - I was \{BLANK\} 403 \{BLANK\}
 Oh, and we used to have fun and games like - the teachers used to - I sees there's one living now that's - that was my Band of Hope teacher - she was - she was an Miss Edwin - and she's still alive today. She must be nearly ninety.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you belong to any other club organised by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Any special treats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Er - you mean ........?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Special Outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Er - Band of Hope used to have a special outing, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 But not otherwise?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 By whom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 By my mother - 'cos my father wasn't always there, you see what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - very deeply.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Conservative - definite. Well absolutely - and so am I and always will be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Why do you think he held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Have you any idea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well .... I suppose you know - you could get a job if you knew the right people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And I think the right people - er - eighty out of a hundred were Tories, weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I suppose so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 The old Liberals - they were all right but - that's why I think - my father's people voted Tory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Ooh she never held any views.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 She wasn't interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - wasn't interested.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember your mother and father voting in a general election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, oh yes. They wouldn't miss.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 They wouldn't miss?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. Used to go down the old Guild hall there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would they both vote the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes. They weren't secretive then like they are now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And they'd vote Conservative would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 They never had two faces under one hat the old people, Madam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would they vote Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
In some places at that time men felt that they risked losing their jobs if they voted differently from their employers. Do you know if your father felt himself under that kind of pressure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
No - I don't think he did because he was a man - he had a pretty secure job on the railway and that didn't involve him, did it, being on the railway - they never even paid any out of work pay for years and years - I can remember that coming i
n because they wasn't supposed to lose their job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Really. Was your father a member of a political party?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did he ever work for a party at an election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Well - you know - er - my mother never had a lot of spare time and I don't think any old people did have spare time - their spare time was taken up by mending clothes - they couldn't just chuck it aside and go and buy new - they had to repair it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When your father was not working at his job he went up to the allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - and he used to like a pot or two of beer - get in company and have a pint or two of beer, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 He used to leave off at six o'clock - start at six and leave off at six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And he was home soon after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes he was home about twenty past - have a cup of tea and up the garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - after he came back from the garden he'd come in and put his tools away, go down the pub and have a pint of beer and then come 
- about half past nine he'd come home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did he attend any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. No. He never believed in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 But he went regularly to have his glass of beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 At the same pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your mother ever go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. No - my mother never drunk - she wasn't never - never did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your father take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. Not as I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 He never attended the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no, no. I - I - only thing I can remember him being in the tug-o-war team. That's all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did he bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. He - my father didn't bet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your mother or father belong to any savings club? Like a boot club or sick club or funeral club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes yes. My father belonged to the West Surrey Benefits. That was a sick club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would that include funeral expenses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. And then you said your mother got clothes for the family through this tally man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That was a sort of club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did you get on with your brother and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh about the ordinary you know. Had our ups and downs but - oh we weathered the old storm between us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was there one you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. I can't say that I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 As a child - who did you play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - I - I on - perhaps I didn't ought to say it - can you turn it off -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So sometimes you played with neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Where did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, mostly in the street - if we didn't want to go up on the fields.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 In other peoples homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, in peoples back yards, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Anywhere else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What games did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Cricket and football. That's about all there was you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes, my mother never made any - anything - go on in there and get and have a wash that's all she said.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were you free to play with anyone you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents discourage you from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 At times - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Why would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - I suppose something happened - they didn't agree with and that was that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I should now like to ask you about you spent your free t
ime when you were at school? Did you have any hobbies then? I think you said you kept a rat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - tame rats - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have any other hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh rabbits - I even kept mice, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have a cat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582007\charrsid14556233 couple}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233  cats.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Dog?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. We never had a dog.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you collect anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Used to go bird egg - bird nesting sometimes you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I was asking you if you collected anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Birds eggs, yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you do any gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Very little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you go for walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you bicycle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh two or three of them that had bikes - but they was a bit of a luxury at that time of day you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Only football. I used to play a lot of football. From the school - which was Charlotteville.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you go to any theatres?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - quite a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 The Guildford theatre?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. But of
 course that's getting back to 1913 - the Guildford theatre - but I used to go before that - when the borough hall - what they used to call the penny pop - that used to be of a Saturday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Just a Saturday night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever go to any concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Er .... no I can't say I do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582007\charrsid14556233 Music Hall}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, music hall, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Where would that be - in Guildford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That'd be in Guildford - and I have been in Aldershot - the old Hippodrome.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Cinema?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - because how I used to go to Aldershot was if I happened to be over with me aunty and me uncle would take me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes of course. Would this be while you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents give you pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. Oh, I might have had tuppence or a penny about once a fortnight, that's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would that be regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. My father when he was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233  he only earned eighteen shillings a week, you know, Madam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Can you remember what you spent the money on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh Liquorice - liquorice all}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582007\charrsid14556233  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 sorts or what they called a calleybonker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Whatever was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 It was a sort of a glorified sugar like, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did anyone outside the home help your mother look after the house or family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - but my mother had a - a lot 
of good friends that used to live up - business people - along the Harvey Road and they knew her conditions and they were very sympathetic to her - even one person I can name especially. The man that painted gates here - the town gate now - course the old
 people are dead and gone - you know - but they were very good to my mother - very good, yes. Used to - well - use to .........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 In what sort of way would they help?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 In the food line.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh in the food line.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Er - yes - anything like - butter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes a little bit of luxury.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes that's right, yes. Very good to my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about your relations? Had you any relations near by?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, I've got two sons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, I meant when you were a child. Had your mother got any relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes - er - her brother lived in the same road as - er - in the same area, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would you see much of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - they used to be in pretty frequent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would her friends and neighbours come in to see her regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Yes - they used to pop over very often - specially if they wanted a tanner - if you hadn't got a tanner and if you could borrow a tanner you could buy a dinner with it, Madam, for your family - it don't make sense do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, not today it doesn't, does it? If your mother was ill or confined to bed, at home how did she manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh the neighbours always used to come in. Oh yes - very good - they were very good all round to one another that time day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you know how she managed when your brother and sister and you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well ........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she ever tell you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
No, I can't say she did, but I should imagine by what I heard later on in life, that they had a pretty rough time, you know what I mean, it was very difficult.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I wondered if somebody would come in to look after, for instance, your brother and sister when you were born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That would be a neighbour would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I thought you meant financially see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No I was thinking .......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I was thinking of managing .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, oh the neighbours - neighbours that time of day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When your relatives came would they come to your house or would you go to their house as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 My mother never used to go out a lot - they always used to come and see us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Mmm. She was a proper home bird - you know, she liked her own home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You said that your mother had some very good friends. Where did she see them? Did she go to see them or did they come to see her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - they used to see her - er - when they used to come up or down the hill - and - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about your father, did he have some friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No my father wasn't much of a - they call a - he looked after himself - minded his own business - you know what I mean - that type of man.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they share any of the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes. Oh my mother could have in who she liked in the house, you know. Oh yes, my father never interfered. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 But she also had some friends of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Where would your father see his friends. In your house, or would he meet them down at the pub or somewhere like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 The only friends my father had was when he went down and had a drink. He knew everybody but my father never got inv
olved in people, you know what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did he ever bring them home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were your mother's friends ever invited into the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would they be offered anything to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, first thing they done was a cup of tea. And a jam tart mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would they come on any particular day or special occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well if there was a Christening or birthday or anything like that or a wedding
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So I think from what you said the friends invited in were mainly your mother's friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did the friends call in casually without an invitation sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, they used to open the door and walk in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 The same as the neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents ever go out to visit friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not a lot.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
People often tell us today that it those day they made their own amusements. What do you think your parents did when they got together with their friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - I know - about Christmas time and - er - anybody 
had an occasion for - a birthday - cor I should think we did have a good old sing-song. We used to let the roof go. They enjoyed themselves - made ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 This was singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Somebody got on the old piano - if you was lucky enough to have one in the home that you were - or ........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - we never had one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Many people divide society into different social classes or groups. In that time before 1918 did you think of some people belonging to
 one group and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Er - no, I don't think we - er - it was always under the surface but it was never - you never let go, you see - I don't think - I don't think er - there was er - er - you knew it was there but you just took it as it ca
me you knew you couldn't do without them, they were your bread and butter - they were providing you with a job and you thought well that's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What sort of groups were you conscious of in those days? I think you said you were taught to lift your cap to the doctor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And health visitor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well can you tell me what sort of groups you were aware of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well we - er - lets see - doctor - define that .......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well let's go on. Which group would you say that you belonged to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I - I just lost the ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Thread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You felt that you looked up I think you said to people who were business men?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What sort of people belonged to this same group as yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What would the men do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
The working class - yes - but that time of day the working classes used to look up to his employer - and they respected him - they really respected him they did that time of day.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So you were brought up to treat people of one group differently from another? For instance you touched your cap I think you said.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And you showed respect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And this would be to the doctor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 To the clergyman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you say the health visitor or somebody like this? The nurse or .......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - er - not so much that - those two particular persons - the Parson and the doctor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would there be anyone you called Sir? Or Madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I was always brought up that way - I do today. I've never lost it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would you call anyone Master
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Just Sir or Madam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I never said Mr. and I don't today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes - quite a lot of it. Oh yes. Amongst the good class people too. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 In the district where you lived - who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Where we lived was a man - Alderman Baker - and he had a big dairy and he - he - after a few years he was Ma
yor of Guildford - he was Mayor of Guildford in 1908. And he was the most respected man in the area I lived in the Trinity area - and that was a pretty big area. He was a very well respected man and he owned Guildford theatre - well he reorganised it what
 was the Borough Hall in 1913
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And did you come into contact with him at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes - he was always approachable - if anybody wanted to see him he was always approachable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Why were they considered important? Because of their job or ...... because of their work in the town or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I certainly think it was a little bit of - a better education. That's only my idea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about the shopkeepers - who did they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh they were far more - er - they wasn't offhanded 
like they are today because they were working for theirself, understand my meaning. They had a certain leaning towards their customer and they served him as the best as they could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would they associated with the clergy and doctors?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. Business men, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about farmers - did you know any farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Didn't know any farmers - but they always seemed a little bit aloof, I don't know why. Don't know why. to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about employers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh I don't think the employer was bad - not in my time - I always had a fair deal from them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And would they associate with the clergy and doctors as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What sort of people would you say went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh that's a pretty ........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would it be the more educated people do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - a lot more working people went to church today - er - then than what they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would it make any difference if they went to Chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I don't think so. I think that's a lot of old bogey, you know, if a working man went to church he was snubbed - I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That wasn't your experience?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - wasn't my experience.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were there many Roman Catholics living around you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not around me, but quite a few there was in Guildford then - quite a few.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was there any friction between the Roman Catholics and the church people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, I know my - we used to say 'Ooh he's a Catholic'. We had some Catholics living next door to us. And I remember my mother's words was
 'Ooh they're Catholics'. My father said 'Well that's - they're Catholics'. Quite funny isn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Where you lived - did all the people in the working class group have the same standard of living? Or would you say there were different levels?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh different levels, oh yes, different levels.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Could you describe a different family from yourselves - from your own, would some of them have more money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well you take a man earning eighteen shillings, like my father did, and another man - well - t
ake a blacksmith - earning about thirty bob - there was still that 'I'm better than you' - in the working class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were some families thought of as rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh a good many.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And other as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember any distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not very pronounced, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No I don't think it worried either of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 They both felt about the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, definitely no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was it possible at that time to move from one group to another? Can you remember anyone who did? Well could get more 
money and so live in a different sort of way? Or become better educated.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - pretty difficult.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Pretty difficult?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Pretty difficult - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember anyone as being described as a real gentleman and a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I've heard it expressed - oh yes. Times out of number.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I think it was the manner of the people. I'd think it was the manner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 The way they treated other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. Their manner to them and - well certain people g
ot their own particular sort of - people that it they can help them they will. Er - different areas there's always a good - good gentleman or a good lady. And I think what they spoke - what they really meant was the kindnesses that they used to do to them
.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You mean such as your mother's friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh we - we didn't think a lot of him - we were more scared of him than anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When you were naughty did your mother ever say 'I'll call a policeman'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How do you think he treated the people?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - well - pretty easy I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - used to come every Monday to collect the rent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What did you feel about him? Do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oooh - no I don't - didn't have any opinion - but I know what our rent was - 6/10.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember feeling as a child that your parents had a struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What did you think about it at the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - I weren't old enough to really .... see what I mean - well ........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Didn't worry you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. But we knew they were having a bad time very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What difference did it make to the family when your father was ill or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well he never had either, Madam, he never - he wasn't a day out of work - and he never had an hour's illness - and I
 never laid in bed an hour, Madam, and that's honest. That's honest - my father never laid in bed an hour with a cold and I thought what a lucky man and I never have so I must be a lucky man, Madam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever get help from the Guardians or the Parish or any charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. It was about - it was obtainable if you wanted - if you asked for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 But you didn't ask for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 It was obtainable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Now, about the time you were at school - would you like a rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were you given lessons by one of your parents before you went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. My oldest brother and sister tried to tell me how to go on. When I first started.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When you first started what time in the morning did you go? And when did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Nine o'clock 'til twelve - twelve to two was dinner time - and then we came out at half past four.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So afternoon school was two 'til half past four?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What kind of school was it? You said it was Charlotteville - that would be a board school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That was a board school - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were there boys and girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I lived next door.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh that was very easy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So it only took you a few minutes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did anyone go with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Where did you have your mid-day meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Indoors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 At home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What would you have to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh - er - we said - er meat ........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 A meat pudding or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. There was no - if you lived too far away from school you had to bring sandwiches.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - first off you didn't like it - but as 
you got older you sort of got used to it and the last two years you woke yourself up and thought 'come on - I got to know something now'. That's how I - that's how it took me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - I can't say I disliked it - I got up to s
tandard seven so I didn't do too bad - that was the highest one there was. Nothing brilliant but - still.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well we had our bits of fun with them you know, but - er they were pretty good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did the teachers emphasise certain things as important in life? Such as manners.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes, that was ........
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh that was their speciality I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 If you did something the teachers disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Out would come that cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And were the girls treated the same as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, there wasn't a lot of distinction. But of course the girls - er - the girls were taken by women that time of day a man
 never took a girls class - they were all women teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And what sort of thing would they cane them for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well insolence as much as anything - or - er - being a bit rough with the other ones, you know, - and wouldn't stand up for themselves. Th
at's all - that's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents show an interest in your school work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes. They used to read the reports - oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they ask you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they ever visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, once or twice, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did the other children come from similar types of home to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes. We were all pretty much of a muchness.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Well I think - er - to be honest I must say yes - because if - one or two people I could name people in this town that went to school with me and they are in business today. They were favoured you know. Oh definitely. 
I mustn't mention names. They were definitely favoured by the teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - human nature being what it is I suppose it's got to happen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was it because they were clever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh no, definitely not clever, no, n
o they were no cleverer than one particular person I could I got in my mind - I was streaks ahead of him. I used to finish up about sixth. Fifth or sixth and he used to finish up about nineteenth - eighteenth or nineteenth, and there was only about twenty
 five in the class.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Only left out of it to my way of thinking because they couldn't grasp it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I don't think it was any - with any intent - they had to be left out because they - well - they were too simple.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 They couldn't keep up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you go on to another school afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would you have stayed longer if you had had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you attend any part time education afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 While you were at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, I used to do errand boy jobs a bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did you get it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Because a shop was down the bottom of our place - down the bottom of the hill, and I went down there three mornings a week like, you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Oh sweep the shop out and scrub the bricks like of a Monday morning and clear up the cellar and help him put a - er - evenings help him put a bit of sugar in - er - out of the two hundredweight bags into two pound bags and the one pound bags.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And what sort of hours would you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh I used to put in about six hours I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have to work on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, I wouldn't work Saturday morning 'cos I wanted to go to football. They wanted me to but I didn't - I wouldn't have it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you work the half day? At all - on Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no - no. No I only done them six hours - that was while I was going to school. See what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What were you paid in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I think I got about a couple bob.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you feel that that was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well ..... 'course we hadn't got that thing poked into our head like they got it today - we took it as a matter of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You didn't question it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I don't think so - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What was it spent on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh used to - to go to the pictures that time of day - the pictures was open in Guildford in th
e - the first one that was built there was the Plaza - that was open I should think round about 1903 I think the Plaza was open.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did you get on with the other people you worked with? Was there anyone apart from your employer? In the shop
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, non, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did he treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you remember how you felt about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No I - didn't have no special praise for him or I didn't - I couldn't condemn him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did you feel about the work - did you like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You didn't like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did the job alter your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No I couldn't say it did - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you do any other part time jobs before you left school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - no. I didn't keep that one too long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Now I'd like to ask you about your first full time job - what was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 My first full time job was apprentice at Puttocks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did you get that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well it was through the kindness of an aunty of mine - my mothe
r's sister saying 'why not do Freddy a good turn, Carry, see if you can get him apprenticed anywhere'. And my father went up to Puttocks and I was apprentice there and it was five bob a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And what exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Oh - er - when you first started it was sweeping out the garage and getting in the ooke for the boilers and clearing all the grease off the chassis and that - but - er - oh they learnt you the trade pretty well. Oh yes - they put me ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I went in the army from there - in 1914.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - what hours did you work at ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh hours - sorry - er - we started at eight and finished at six and we worked 'til four o'clock Saturdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And did you work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have a half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No. Four o'clock Saturday was our half a day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And did you have any holidays - with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - not at that time of day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And you were paid five shillings a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you feel that was a fair wage? Did you accept that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh I was highly honoured to be an apprentice - specially in my walk of life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes - I gave her a few shillings - I can't really remember what it was - but I know - I think she used to give me a couple of bob back.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And what would she spend the money on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I don't know, but if I wanted a pair of overalls and - my mother always bought them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So I expect she put that by.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You think she probably saved it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 But of course my brother was fortunate - my brother and sister were both earning bringing money in to the home then see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And they were still living at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. Makes a lot of difference - I was very, very lucky.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did you get on with the other people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Very well. Severe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 He was severe - he was a hard master but a good one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did you feel about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh I - er I took it in me strike - I was delighted to know that I was going to do something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And how did you feel about the work - did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - I really enjoyed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What other jobs have you done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 When I came out of the army .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You were in the army after Puttocks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Until the end of 18.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 That's right. I went back to Puttocks for about a twelve month driving mail vans all over the country for them when they had a contrac
t for about forty mail vans - as far down as Sussex, Reading, Berkshire and I think I done everything - about a week here and a week there - they were calling up the different men, you know, waiting for them to be demobbed, you see, they wasn't - er - so 
I
 said 'Oh well I've had enough of this, Governor'. So this man, Mr Baker, he started up in a coach business, a Pearl Grey, and I went to - I didn't go to school with him - but he was one of my well to do friends, you know, as I was telling you about, he s
a
ys 'Fred, you're just the bloke I want' he said, now they were starting up coaches and we were going to have lorries, he said 'will you come and work for me'. I said 'what are you going to pay?' He said 'what you been getting now? I said 'fifty bob' - thi
s was in 1918 - not bad money, Madam, fifty shillings. He said 'Well, I'll give you three quid' I said 'right, fair enough.' Well I went and give my notice and I stuck that for quite a few years - driving coaches, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So you had an apprenticeship at Puttocks but did you have a training period for the next job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
No, no. I - I'd learnt - I'd learnt me stuff in oils and learnt me stuff in the army 'cos I still kept on - er - I joined up in the Infantry - there it is now - the old Queens - but I snea
ked me nose in the M.T's - Mechanical Transport. And I was always in .......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So you got a lot of experience while you were in the army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Definitely, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you belong to any Trade Union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, never have.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Some had different - but I think you - well there must be a difference between the two. I think there must be. To my way of thinking.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you feel that there were divisions of interest among the workers as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes. There was, yes. I put it down to jelousy. If you were doing a better job than them they didn't like it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers - did you feel that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
Yes - because they weren't so keen to learn a young boy as what they are today. But you was alright if you poked your nose in, Madam, you know, and had a good look round and see what he was doing. You sort of learnt yourself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You learnt that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would you say that your full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Definitely - after the war yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What sort of way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - you thought there were more in the world - in the - sort of - er - the war made you feel bigger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 But that was the army experience?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your job make you feel any different at Puttocks before you went in the army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh. Oh yes, I had more confidence in myself, oh yes - it sort of uplifts 
you if you can get a job that you know has got something on the end, Madam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Can I ask you a little bit about your life at home after you left school did you continue to live at home until you went in the army?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 None whatever.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Or with your brother and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, none whatever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you spend your Sunday any differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, I must say I no, I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Slightly. Slightly that time of day, but I'm very much involved in politics if I spoke the truth today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You are involved in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Y
es. I'm not - I'm not involved in it - I don't belong to any party but I'm very interested - very interested in it. But I still got my assurances same as I had years ago - still the same they never altered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So you said you took an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Up to a point, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What were your views - the same as your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And was it for the same reason do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - but they - er - what they told me about politics didn't mean a thing - I come to my own conclusions - and I ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So you made up your own mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, yes, they never forced them on me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And did you vote in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Er - well I voted as soon as I was old enough - and you had to be eighteen then didn't you - or was it .......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No twenty one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well I voted as soon as I was able.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever feel under pressure from any one to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Myself I never was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You never were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Because this - they told me what to do as regards politics I said 'Mind your own business, I've got my views and you've got yours'.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Were you ever a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever work for one of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, when I was working for that co
ach people we had a lorry and we took the old liberal man round - name of Cranley - with all the big hoardings up 'Vote Liberal'
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So did you vote Liberal or did you vote Conservative? Did you take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - I can't say I did - I used to enjoy elections - I used to have a bit of fun.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What about your wife - did she have the same views that you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, I think she did because her father was a publican - so he - I think they must be Tories.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you both vote the same then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Do you think she ever felt under any pressure to vote a particular way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No - she was a woman who had a mind of her own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did she ever take part in a political activity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not at election time or any other time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
You told me earlier something of how you spent your spare time - I think you said that you went down to the cinema when it was open - did you continue to spend your spar
e time in the same way when you were working full time or did you start to do different things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well - when I first started like - after the war .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 This was before the war, I was thinking, when you first went to Puttocks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh, oh yes, wh
en I had the money I used to go to the theatre, you know, well - it wasn't a theatre then - it was what we called the old penny pot - you know what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What you mentioned earlier?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And so you would spend a little bit more on entertainment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes - I was a proper boy for that sort of thing - I like entertainment - I do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And you'd go out in the evening would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well, mostly used to toddle on on me own and then see somebody down there see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Meet up with somebody there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you make any new friends when you started full time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, tremendous. Oh yes, different people, different people that you've never seen before, you see, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Boys as well as girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, both.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And did you meet them at your works? Or going out in the evenings when you were going to these amusements?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh we used to meet them going out - we never used to - er 3/8 not in work. Th
ere wasn't any girls employed where I was you see, not in the workshop, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you ever bring your friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes. My mother welcomed her - we got 3/8 I know when - boy at Puttocks same as me - he was going to the Technical night classes 
and - 'cos he was a bit backward - he couldn't grasp it, you know - and used to come up and we used to round on the table - and the old book - the old manual - motor manual you know - not 'cos I say it myself - I was a little bit quick on the uptake - I d
idn't want telling twice you know how. He was - turned out to be a very clever boy but he was more slow, understand my meaning, but he was thorough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have any special friends at this time? Would this boy be a special friend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes he would be, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would there be a special girl friend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Not at - not quite at that time - shortly after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 And where would you go with your special friend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Er - boy or girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well either?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Well it was only that time of day we went in the town, to be honest, or in the castle grounds - all that's closed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes, mmm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did they expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes and if I - said I'm going out with a girl mum, 'Oh bring her home, lets ha
ve I look at her' you know, but I didn't take any home until I got hold of the right one - no. I'd go oooo this one aint no good for my mother - you know, you can weight it up when you get older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, not after I started work, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 What age were you when you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 ?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Twenty eight I should imagine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Twenty eight? And how long had you known your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I courted her for about six and a half years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How did you meet her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Round the river.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. I can remember as if it were only yesterday. Little did I think she was going to become my wife.
