\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No that's my mother. My wife was born in Boxgrove Road, and her father was a butler to Acheson Gray.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you save up money before getting }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did your parents help you in starting up a home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 No, I was fortunate - I always had a good job after the war and I saved my money and I 
saved about one hundred and ten quid and that was a lot of money in that time of day. That was a lot of money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 How long were you engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Ooh I don't know as if we ever had ...... about six months when we decided to get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233  she said 'well do
n't waste some time now' I said 'no'. Her father that time of day was er - a steward at Whipperdell Club but he only went there to get an insight of the pub game because his intentions was to take a pub. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Would you describe your wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
 at Trinity Church. The Reverend Sharp }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15489644 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 
 us - and we got in a coach driven by my governor - Mr Baker - and took us up over to my father-in-law's place - my wife's people - they used to live in Brookwood - oh we had a lovely time. But I co
uldn't go on a honeymoon because we - as they call honeymoon, you know - couldn't go away for a week because you couldn't get a coach driver that time of day, really, they were at a premium, you know, what I mean to say - that knew their way about the cou
ntry, Madam, because they wasn't signposted up like they are - when I first started driving coaches there was only one signpost from here to Bolton and that was the top of Andover Hill - top of Andover.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 So you needed to know your way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 You had to 
sort of be that type of chap to know which way you had to go - and they were a bit difficult to find. Not because I say it but you couldn't lose me round about England now - at my - I - I'd get lost on account of the by passes but I'd find my way there. O
h yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 I expect you had some wedding presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes. The firm gave me a clock.
