\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Oh yes. Ooh I suppose we had about thirty or forty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179139 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5067690 FR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3022118\charrsid14556233 Yes.
